## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on available online resources, which may not encompass all aspects of nursing research. Additionally, some sources may not be peer-reviewed, potentially affecting the reliability of the information. The search was also limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant research published in other languages.

